8-07/">Proterra</a>在努力削减成本后于 8 月申请破产保护。据 Volta Trucks 称，这一事件的转变减少了其计划生产的车辆数量，并使筹集继续运营所需的资金变得更加困难。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>电动汽车行业面临大量裁员和倒闭，尤其是在不断发展（且供应链问题困扰）领域的初创企业。 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lordstown-motors-sues-foxconn-and-declares-bankruptcy-100549575.html">Lordstown Motors 在营业五年后于 2023 年中期宣布破产</a>，而<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cash-strapped-ev-startup-arrival-is-laying-off-half-its-staff-172255412.html">Arrival 则经历了多轮裁员</a>，所有迹象都表明将要破产——仅举两个例子。与洛兹敦汽车公司的情况一样，沃尔特卡车公司可以为其现有技术寻找买家。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/ev-startup-volta-trucks-files-for-bankruptcy-115059284.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/ev-startup-volta-trucks-files-for-bankruptcy-115059284.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 91ce709a-a4b8-478a-87d1-3d5c2b8fae57</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 11:50:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1697542778</ingested><modified> 2023-10-17T11:39:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-05/eb9a4510-cc87-11ec-bfee-e018b0138366" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazo