鬼”是一种夜间活动的生物，白天会变成石头。马扎。该氏族曾居住在苏格兰的一座城堡中，后来被人类背叛并被诅咒被冻结在石头里。一千年后，石像鬼在纽约醒来，并选择在夜间充当其保护者。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当然，真人版<em>《石像鬼》</em>是好事还是坏事取决于到目前为止你对迪士尼翻拍作品的喜爱程度。我们只能希望道伯曼和万的公司能够公正地呈现这部剧，特别是因为它很可能会使用大量的计算机生成图像来忠实于源材料。迪士尼最近因其使用 CGI 技术而受到了很多批评，评论家认为 CGI 技术在视觉上没有吸引力，而且效果不佳，包括在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.vox.com/culture/23730350/little-mermaid-remake-review-halle-bailey-visuals"><em>《小美人鱼》</em></a>和漫威的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Marvel/comments/113a075/antman_and_the_wasp_quantumania_disappointed_cgi/"><em>《蚁人2：黄蜂女现身量子狂热》等</em></a>电影中。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/disney-is-making-a-live-action-gargoyles-show-with-james-wan-100025832.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/disney-is-making-a-live-action-gargoyles-show-with-james-wan-100025832.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8c95b02d-1ddd-4346-94a8-319c8b741bfe</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:00:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1697536795</ingested><modified> 2023-10-17T10:00:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/4404ac40-6cc8-11ee-9e9f-08c3678db28e" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1000" med